eUserRating":4.61723,"languageCodesISO2A":["EN"],"genres":["Travel","Navigation"],"sellerName":"MARINETRAFFIC APPLICATIONS LTD","artistId":1668374750,"artistName":"MarineTraffic Applications LTD","price":0.0,"bundleId":"com.marinetraffic.ios","primaryGenreName":"Travel","primaryGenreId":6003,"releaseDate":"2012-10-08T07:00:00Z","trackId":563910324,"trackName":"MarineTraffic - Ship Tracking","genreIds":["6003","6010"],"currentVersionReleaseDate":"2026-04-08T02:30:50Z","releaseNotes":"Bug fixes and map improvements.","version":"5.2.0","wrapperType":"software","currency":"NOK","description":"Welcome to MarineTraffic. \n \nYou spoke, we listened. Based on feedback from our customers, the MarineTraffic app has been updated to deliver a faster, clearer, and more reliable way to track vessels and monitor maritime activity worldwide. \n\nMarineTraffic is used by maritime professionals, shipping companies, port authorities, and enthusiasts around the world. With MarineTraffic 2.0, the experience you rely on has been improved, while keeping the core tools you already know and trust. \n\nIf you’ve used MarineTraffic before, you’ll feel at home straight away. The main features remain familiar, now supported by better performance, clearer maps, and a more stable foundation built for the future. \n\n \n\nWith MarineTraffic, you can: \n\nTrack vessels live worldwide using AIS data \n\nView ship positions, movements, and voyage history with key events along the route \n\nBuild and monitor your chosen fleet by following specific vessels \n\nAccess detailed vessel information such as type, destination, speed, and course \n\nExplore enhanced maps with close weather monitoring, including wind conditions \n\n \n\nA unified MarineTraffic experience \n\nThe new MarineTraffic brings core tools together into one unified mobile app experience. The new app focuses on clarity, reliability, and ease of use, improving performance while keeping the experience familiar. \n\nMaps load faster, interactions feel smoother, and information is presented more clearly, supporting both everyday use and professional maritime workflows. \n\n \n\nWhat’s improved in MarineTraffic: \n\nFaster performance across maps and weather views \n\nClearer visuals and smoother interactions throughout the app \n\nImproved platform stability and reliability \n\nAll your key tools in one app, including close weather monitoring \n\n \n\nUnlock more with the Mobile Pro Plan \n\nThe Mobile Pro Plan brings advanced capabilities together for users who need deeper visibility and extended coverage. \n\nWith Mobile Pro, you can: \n\nTrack vessels beyond coastal coverage using Satellite AIS, including activity in open oceans \n\nAccess advanced fleet monitoring tools for wider oversight \n\nFollow vessels with extended historical data and deeper insights \n\nGain access to additional maritime data layers for professional use \n\nMobile Pro expands your vessel tracking capabilities when standard AIS coverage is not enough. \n\nMobile Pro is designed for users who need a broader, more complete view of global vessel movement. \n\n \n\nDesigned for real-world use \n\nMarineTraffic is used in many different ways, from fleet management to vessel tracking. MarineTraffic is designed to support these use cases without adding unnecessary complexity. \n\nYou can follow vessels and fleets important to you, set up alerts, and explore global vessel traffic in real time. Vessel details, voyage history, and close weather monitoring are accessible in one place, helping you stay informed without switching between tools. \n\n \n\nMarineTraffic builds on everything users already rely on, with a faster, clearer, and more dependable mobile experience designed to support maritime activity around the world. \n\nDownload MarineTraffic to explore global vessel traffic with improved speed, clarity, and reliability.","sellerUrl":"https://www.marinetraffic.com/","trackContentRating":"4+","fileSizeBytes":"107004928","formattedPrice":"Free","userRatingCountForCurrentVersion":26836,"averageUserRatingForCurrentVersion":4.61723,"isVppDeviceBasedLicensingEnabled":true,"userRatingCount":26836}